prompts.frontCover: Front cover of a birthday card for Johnny from Jordan. A charming, humorous cartoon-style illustration of a slightly grumpy-looking, very fluffy cat wearing a tiny, lopsided birthday party hat. The cat is sitting next to a single, oversized slice of birthday cake that is almost as big as it is. A single, wobbly candle with a brightly lit flame is on the cake. The cat has a thought bubble above its head containing a simple, crudely drawn fish skeleton. The text "Happy Birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script, positioned centrally across the middle of the scene. The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a vibrant watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures.
